race.description: 2026 Inglis Yearling Sales Series F&M Handicap
race.comment: KILKENNY (13) only the one win from six starts and like the way she closed late over the 1200m when fifth at Warwick Farm. Looking for this trip and further now and will be hard to hold out with the 52.5kg. Genuine each way player. CHANGING COLOURS (2) above average mare who returned good closing splits first-up when a gritty second over 1300m at Rosehill. Will keep improving as she steps out in trip and gets Grima's 3kg claim. Look for her late. CINSAULT (11) thrown in the deep end today after returning with a tough victory over 1200m at Canterbury in BM64 class. Maps well and stays in the mix despite the short price. YES LULU (1) pulled up with cardiac arrhythmia when a dismal last over 1400m at this track. Blinkers come off and will appreciate Roper's claim and the fast tempo. Expected to be in the finish. VIENNA VIXEN (6) got out late when fifth over this course and distance at latest. Fitter now and she looks over the odds.
